Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:23.56,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰かを悲しませてまで　笑えなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.71,0:03:34.31,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう言って彼女はうつむいてたんだ　夜に泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:41.90,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷たく貼り付いて　凍えている
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:48.86,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降り続く現実に　傘などない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:55.60,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生きてゆくことが　戦いなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:59.33,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そんな理由だけで　閉じ込められた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.43,0:04:02.22,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Heart　My Story
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:09.71,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泪のムコウが見えるの　輝いている
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:16.41,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小さな窓には　あの頃みたいに　青い空が映る
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.68,0:04:23.16,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ah  ah　鳥のように　飛べはしないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:34.64,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰かを悲しませたとき　感じる痛み
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.77,0:04:36.42,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘れないように
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:42.00,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そっと目を閉じて　泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:20.96,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若能换人不再悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:23.56,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我宁愿舍弃笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.71,0:03:27.41,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}她说着低下了头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.51,0:03:34.31,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这一夜 我流泪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:41.90,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冰冷彻骨 仿如冻雨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:48.86,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}洒落的现实 无处可避
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:55.60,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生存就是战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:59.33,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}仅为这理由而束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.43,0:04:02.22,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}My Heart  My Story
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:09.71,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泪光对面 看到了光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:16.41,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}小小的窗上 映出旧时晴空
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.68,0:04:23.16,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}虽无法如鸟儿一般飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:36.42,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}为铭记谁人悲伤之时的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:42.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}轻轻闭上双眼 哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:55.71,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(153,361)}{\3a&HC9&\4c&H000000&\1c&HFEFDFF&}为了未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.28,0:00:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎能够理解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.56,0:00:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊欧利亚·舒恩伯格制造Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.21,0:00:10.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 制造GN Drive的缘由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.61,0:00:12.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.50,0:00:15.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武力介入是为此铺路的基石
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.58,0:00:17.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊欧利亚的目的是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.30,0:00:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将人类引向新纪元
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:25.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 我…正面临着变革
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.16,0:00:27.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变革?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你达到的极致吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.43,0:00:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天人再次…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.71,0:00:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时请务必给我战斗的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:46.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复仇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.07,0:00:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所追求的是战斗之人才能到达的极限
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.45,0:00:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年曾说我扭曲了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.86,0:01:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 他也是只能战斗的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:06.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才渴求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.90,0:01:08.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.86,0:01:15.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那极致的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.99,0:01:17.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只渴望胜利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.87,0:01:19.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外还有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.58,0:01:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有通向未来的…明天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.00,0:01:35.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格杀勿论
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.14,0:01:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空手入白刃?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是 我的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.81,0:02:15.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗吧 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.83,0:02:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将我劈开 亲手获得胜利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:30.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.38,0:02:31.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何不给我致命一击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.31,0:02:33.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着抓住明天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.86,0:02:43.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为生存而战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈 路易丝·阿勒威的机体呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:56.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没反应 应该是撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.23,0:02:58.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:02:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.90,0:03:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是想谢你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.76,0:03:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为纯种觉醒了吗 刹那·F·清英
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.44,0:03:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是掌握人类命运的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道Veda所在了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:56.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 王留美给的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:04:59.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到Veda了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗号解析完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐标是CZ9842R 月球背面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.81,0:05:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜 用超望远摄像机捕捉坐标
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.01,0:05:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉格朗日2
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:16.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未进行殖民地开发的地点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.47,0:05:17.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要藏身再适合不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.32,0:05:19.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显示坐标
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.27,0:05:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.48,0:05:26.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将这个位置的天体图重叠上去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:31.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星体的位置偏了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光学迷彩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.36,0:05:36.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计算出有偏差的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离是…直径15千米
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15千米?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.13,0:05:48.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要如此隐藏的物体…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在月球背面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.38,0:06:01.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐 实验室的运输舰发来暗号通信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.85,0:06:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新装备来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.62,0:06:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独立治安维持部队A-LAWS\N全军动员开始歼灭天人作战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:21.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒他们这反政府势力最后的要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为统一世界赢得真正的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.50,0:06:28.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待诸位奋勇作战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:35.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,21艘巡洋舰加108架MS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:37.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这么多战力…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.97,0:06:41.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准将 特许员脱离了舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:45.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别理他们 要在战场上肆意妄为可受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利冯兹发来了返航命令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:54.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他终于下定决心了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:56.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 一切按计划进行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.78,0:06:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该来的已经迫近了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:03.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝·阿勒威
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:14.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为家人报仇? 我又何尝不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.11,0:07:17.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为天下就你可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.24,0:07:24.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活该
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.02,0:07:31.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能充当战力的都带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam各机的强化组件 还有托勒密的补充物资
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.26,0:07:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连0 Gundam都带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.07,0:07:44.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安装了粒子储存罐 可以在一定时间内进行战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 尽快搬入
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.43,0:07:48.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.43,0:07:54.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王留美指定的坐标上有舰队集结
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错了 Veda就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:08:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有变革者的大本营
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要突破A-LAWS舰队 夺回Veda
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会是前所未有的激战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:14.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去 为了完成我的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:15.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库斯洛德君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.02,0:08:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定了 不再犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也参加
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:22.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索玛·比利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有参战的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.13,0:08:31.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 虽然目的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.70,0:08:33.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们都有奔赴战场的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.37,0:08:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这意志通往未来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.59,0:08:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要为未来而战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:52.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了从变革者的支配下解放人类
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:58.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让我和索玛·比利斯这种人 不再出现在世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:02.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的任务是打倒联邦政府
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要狙击变革者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.97,0:09:06.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:09.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要变革
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不变革就无法面对未来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.96,0:09:19.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,补给完成后就发动托勒密
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.97,0:09:20.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在托勒密没有操舵员…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:30.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.65,0:09:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然能行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:43.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.70,0:09:45.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去月球背面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉娜殿下 好多星星哦
