Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只狐狸精…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.73,0:19:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镇压! 他们是反政府势力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.63,0:19:44.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:50.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方部队正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.02,0:19:52.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS队 开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.29,0:19:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不死之身的戈拉索瓦 前来拜访
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.28,0:20:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对付运输舰为何如此狼狈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.81,0:20:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们躲在僚舰身后 无法攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.31,0:20:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队不需要累赘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连同敌舰一起击沉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.27,0:20:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰上还有我方士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.41,0:20:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我命令你开火
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.54,0:20:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准将 敌舰突破了反粒子领域
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.16,0:20:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.84,0:20:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00-Raiser 驱逐目标
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.25,0:20:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快想办法!
