Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.27,0:22:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好壮观
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.85,0:22:40.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯他们正在战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.28,0:22:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争之光…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.46,0:22:49.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS舰队被突破…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.99,0:22:53.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来人类挺喜欢战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.05,0:22:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不正是你一手安排的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.87,0:23:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引导他们走到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.25,0:23:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这应该也是你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.87,0:23:04.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.32,0:23:06.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.80,0:23:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你们的上等种族
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.22,0:23:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可称之为创造主
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.39,0:23:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你的狼子野心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.88,0:23:21.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透过脑量子波早已清晰可见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.43,0:23:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜了 雷杰尼·雷杰塔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.32,0:23:35.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利冯兹·阿尔马克
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.11,0:23:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我…只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.23,0:23:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够引导人类的只有我…
